@startuml
title Discretionary Access Control (DAC)

hide circle
hide empty members
skinparam backgroundColor transparent



class User {
  +userId: String
  +name: String
}

class Resource {
  +resourceId: String
  +name: String
}

class OwnerPermission {
  +read: Boolean
  +write: Boolean
  +execute: Boolean
}

User "1" -- "0..*" Resource : owns >
User "1" -- "0..*" OwnerPermission : receives >
Resource "1" -- "0..*" OwnerPermission : for >

note right of OwnerPermission
Owner (or delegated user)
assigns permissions
to specific users.
end note

@enduml